@MovieManager.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5212
@ContentType = application/json
# After successful login, set @AuthToken to the received token (e.g. Authorization: Bearer <token>)

### ========== CREATE USER (REGISTER) ==========
### Create a new user account with username "Huzair"
POST {{MovieManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "username": "shams",
  "email": "shams@example.com",
  "password": "Shams@123",
  "role":"Admin"
}

###

### ========== LOGIN (get JWT) ==========
### Login as demo user (admin or user) to receive JWT token
POST {{MovieManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

###

### ========== GET ALL MOVIES ==========
### Retrieve all movies from the database
GET {{MovieManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/movies
Accept: {{ContentType}}

###

### ========== CREATE NEW MOVIE ==========
### Create a new movie (example 1) - requires Admin role
POST {{MovieManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/movies
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

{
  "title": "The Shawshank Redemption",
  "director": "Frank Darabont",
  "genre": "Drama",
  "releaseDate": "1994-10-14T00:00:00Z",
  "rating": 9.3
}

###

### Create another movie (example 2) - requires Admin role
POST {{MovieManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/movies
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

{
  "title": "Inception",
  "director": "Christopher Nolan",
  "genre": "Science Fiction",
  "releaseDate": "2010-07-16T00:00:00Z",
  "rating": 8.8
}

###

### Create third movie (example 3) - requires Admin role
POST {{MovieManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/movies
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

{
  "title": "The Dark Knight",
  "director": "Christopher Nolan",
  "genre": "Action",
  "releaseDate": "2008-07-18T00:00:00Z",
  "rating": 9.0
}

###

### ========== GET MOVIE BY ID ==========
### Retrieve a specific movie by ID (replace MOVIE_ID with actual UUID)
@movieId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

GET {{MovieManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/movies/{{movieId}}
Accept: {{ContentType}}

###

### ========== UPDATE MOVIE ==========
### Update an existing movie (replace MOVIE_ID with actual UUID) - requires Admin role
PUT {{MovieManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/movies/{{movieId}}
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

{
  "title": "The Shawshank Redemption - Updated",
  "director": "Frank Darabont",
  "genre": "Drama",
  "releaseDate": "1994-10-14T00:00:00Z",
  "rating": 9.4
}

###

### ========== DELETE MOVIE ==========
### Delete a movie by ID (replace MOVIE_ID with actual UUID) - requires Admin role
DELETE {{MovieManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/movies/{{movieId}}
Accept: {{ContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

###

### ========== SEARCH BY TITLE ==========
### Search movies by title (case-insensitive partial match)
GET {{MovieManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/movies/search/title/Shawshank
Accept: {{ContentType}}

###

### Search for "Inception"
GET {{MovieManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/movies/search/title/Inception
Accept: {{ContentType}}

###

### Search for movies with "the" in title
GET {{MovieManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/movies/search/title/the
Accept: {{ContentType}}

###

### ========== SEARCH BY DIRECTOR ==========
### Search movies by director name (case-insensitive partial match)
GET {{MovieManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/movies/search/director/Christopher%20Nolan
Accept: {{ContentType}}

###

### Search for "Frank Darabont"
GET {{MovieManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/movies/search/director/Frank%20Darabont
Accept: {{ContentType}}

###

### ========== SEARCH BY GENRE ==========
### Search movies by genre (case-insensitive partial match)
GET {{MovieManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/movies/search/genre/Drama
Accept: {{ContentType}}

###

### Search for action movies
GET {{MovieManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/movies/search/genre/Action
Accept: {{ContentType}}

###

### Search for sci-fi movies
GET {{MovieManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/movies/search/genre/Science%20Fiction
Accept: {{ContentType}}

###

### ========== ERROR TESTING ==========
### Test: Get non-existent movie (should return 404)
GET {{MovieManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/movies/ffffffff-ffff-ffff-ffff-ffffffffffff
Accept: {{ContentType}}

###

### Test: Create movie with invalid data (missing required fields - should return 400) - requires Admin role
POST {{MovieManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/movies
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

{
  "title": "",
  "director": "",
  "genre": "Drama",
  "releaseDate": "1994-10-14T00:00:00Z",
  "rating": 9.3
}

###

### Test: Create movie with invalid rating (should return 400) - requires Admin role
POST {{MovieManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/movies
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

{
  "title": "Test Movie",
  "director": "Test Director",
  "genre": "Drama",
  "releaseDate": "1994-10-14T00:00:00Z",
  "rating": 15
}

###

### Test: Search with empty title (should return 400)
GET {{MovieManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/movies/search/title/
Accept: {{ContentType}}

###

